These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: cranberry, potato
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person eating cranberry##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Food      | cranberry  | potato   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, russian
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the malaysian is the person driving the tram##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Nationality   | russian | malaysian  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, card-games
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Hobby    | card-games     | fishing |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

