The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific
2 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, july
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the project-manager is in an even position##4
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |        2        |
